Net-Rovio version 1.5
======================

CHANGES

In 1.5: Added lights_blue function, changed Docs again. 
In 1.4: Made several more changes to the documentation to clarify
In 1.3: Made several changes to the documentation to clarify
In 1.2: Added many additional functions from the Rovio API.
In 1.1: Switched from WWW::Mechanize to LWP::Simple for simplicity, added send_photo()
In 0.9: A second argument for send() is optional
In 0.8: Prerequisite for WWW::Mechanize added

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::Simple

